biography: Tommy is a golfer hailing from Espoo Ringside Golf. Known for his calm demeanor on the course, Tommy approaches each shot with a calculated precision that belies his otherwise jovial nature off the green.

A competitor in past Hector Trophée tournaments, Tommy is looking forward to participating in Hector Trophée 2025. This upcoming tournament will mark Tommy's third appearance in the competition. While victory has eluded him thus far, Tommy's determination remains unwavering.
Tommy is still actively involved in Hector events and is expected to be a strong contender in the upcoming tournament.
